版<br />\n<br />\n所以你有興趣都係 email 我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nhkgmarty@gmail.com"},{"pid":"6560cb6e0810218f7f79884d35f7f2950f4f1ce7","tid":55684,"uid":25136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見得閒講多兩句順便推post<br />\n<br />\n依家離考試都仲有三個月，好似好快就考但其實實際上係好多時間黎<br />\n你問好多人讀緊大學既，其實好多大學既course 都係最後就考果幾日先至由頭到尾重新學番曬，所以如果你真心肯由依家開始chur，除左language 我好肯定你仲有時間進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而第一步我要說服你既係，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有讀ict 既真係值得擺多d 時間</strong></span></span><br />\n咁多年我d 學生都覺得真係值得，相比起其他科擺好少既時間入去，你會得到好大既提升，因為真係你睇下同其他科比較下，呢科真係相對易好多，我唔想hea你我用例子答你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/11149723_460610950766992_6484006278058194345_o.jpg?oh=50c5f2421b4ed4dc6aa14fa5114ab2a5&amp;amp;oe=58D8BC1C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F11149723_460610950766992_6484006278058194345_o.jpg%3Foh%3D50c5f2421b4ed4dc6aa14fa5114ab2a5%26amp%3Boe%3D58D8BC1C&h=92deff9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗呢個世界係得ict 會出d 咁撚on9 既題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n所以你信我，我自己當年係由3個elective drop 到single elective，就係ict呢科，我對呢科咁有信心，係因為我知呢科真係好容易拎到高分，特別係讀書一般既同學，呢科真係可以打救上u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再續</blockquote><br />\n兩個人報有無得平啲？<br />\n<br />\n同埋你一個 elective入到 u咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他科好好？順便問下你點温書</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nICT5*  polyu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  best5 19分 <br />\n利申 認真易拎高分 無乜點溫都5* 好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd3bc26186354047a4c527c824d214a62181940","tid":55684,"uid":26350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T16:48:09.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6783690c464a8430f4bdd213e40953e8f821e0be","tid":55684,"uid":37264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:45:11.000Z","msg":"又上嚟搵生意, 單獨一科考個5**就出嚟R人補習, 呢度大把高手啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"40e3f99bbe05a3c0bbd336f25f371b51424a0981","tid":55684,"uid":67606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:54:42.000Z","msg":"過主啦上黎搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20fa60980c81c3ee4a4c808b6df2212067b1e78","tid":55684,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又上嚟搵生意, 單獨一科考個5**就出嚟R人補習, 呢度大把高手啦屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗我都可以試下，某u cs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a349b46e40a45f7060a055caf4f79ceac2e99e31","tid":55684,"uid":37264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:28:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又上嚟搵生意, 單獨一科考個5**就出嚟R人補習, 呢度大把高手啦屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗我都可以試下，某u cs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係CS人但係做dev, 當年自修裸考電腦科A, 打過OI比賽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中學電腦科係真係弱智的"},{"pid":"cec346d9b0dc7927c3ce17241be21626fcc28d47","tid":55684,"uid":10586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T05:43:17.000Z","msg":"垃圾樓主<br />\n拖左我地成兩個月時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor